\c 179 
\pc \bd 17\bd*\bd 9\bd*

\s NINACHUNGA USIKU NA MCHANA
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Ninachunga usiku na mchana, kusikia sauti ya Bwana Mungu, kama jinsi Mungu alikua, akitembelea Adamu jioni.\bd*
\pc \bdit Bwana akiniita nami nitaitika Baba, Bwana akinituma, nitaenda pote ambapo ananituma, ninakaa kama mlinzi nikuchunga kusikia sauti ya Bwana Mungu ikifariji roho yangu\bdit*\bd .\bd*
\zoli1 \bd Ninachunga usiku na mchana, kama zamu angojavyo asubuhi kusikia sauti ya Baba Mungu ili anambie habari za Ufalme.\bd*
\pc \bdit Bwana akiniita nami nitaitika Baba, Bwana akinituma, nitaenda pote ambapo ananituma, ninakaa kama mlinzi nikuchunga kusikia sauti ya Bwana Mungu ikifariji roho yangu\bdit*\bd .\bd*
\zoli1 \bd Ninachunga usiku na mchana, kusikia sauti ya Baba Mungu, anambie habari za kuja kwake, nijue habari za Ufalme.\bd*
\pc \bdit Bwana akiniita nami nitaitika Baba, Bwana akinituma, nitaenda pote ambapo ananituma, ninakaa kama mlinzi nikuchunga kusikia sauti ya Bwana Mungu ikifariji roho yangu\bdit*\bd .\bd*
\zoli1 \bd Ninasimama juu ya mnara, nikichunga kusikia sauti ya Baba, anambie ambacho nitafanya katika giza hii ya dunia.\bd*
\pc \bdit Bwana akiniita nami nitaitika Baba, Bwana akinituma, nitaenda pote ambapo ananituma, ninakaa kama mlinzi nikuchunga kusikia sauti ya Bwana Mungu ikifariji roho yangu\bdit*\bd .\bd*
